,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T06:59:47.000Z","msg":"Binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ab05f41aae98d3aaf1908008b9dfc3b43c778e","tid":917811,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T15:10:13.000Z","msg":"呢條友唔多掂 <br />\n可以前覺得佢敢言 依它"}]}